ars\ndue to collisions of HI gas in the LMC. The new numerical simulations of the\ngas dynamics successfully reproduce the current distribution of the\nL-component. This lends theoretical support for the present picture.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 17 Oct 2020 15:49:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Oct 2020 16:02:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-28"}
